{"tid":2211863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蕭美琴自稱「駐美大使」 胡錫進警告軍事行動將升級","createTime":"2020-09-21T11:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T14:46:52.000Z","uid":25468,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"135cf8dcea80d59e92bc55a0906cd5b8c4511ad3","tid":2211863,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SvOwP8hyfpqwGo5nVmrBqw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/ac9e2ae0-fbe9-11ea-abe7-761b0fd9c7fd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSvOwP8hyfpqwGo5nVmrBqw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2Fac9e2ae0-fbe9-11ea-abe7-761b0fd9c7fd&h=9c821f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣駐美代表蕭美琴近日將自己的社交帳號Twitter簡介，更改成「台灣駐美大使（Taiwan Ambassador to the US）」，引起外界關注。她周一（21日）在社交網站Facebook指，自己與美國政府機關互動的正式職銜，仍然是「台北經濟文化代表處代表」，而Twitter簡介的「Ambassador」並非美國官方目前所承認的稱謂。大陸官媒主編胡錫進則<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">警告美台停止勾結，否則大陸的軍事行動必將繼續大幅升級，直至攤牌</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，簡介上的「Ambassador」不但是對現有工作的形容詞，事實上已成為許多美方各界友人稱呼她的方式。雖然並非美國官方目前承認的稱謂，但她在美國代表台灣，實際工作與各國使館無分別，工作量以及與美方互動頻率，甚至比其他國家大使的業務更多及複雜。<br />\n<br />\n蕭美琴指出，7月底到任後一直努力跟各界接觸、溝通、爭取，盼改善台灣長期在國際上碰到的不公平待遇，而在代表處各人的努力下已有所進展，美方對台灣的訴求亦有更多的正面看待。<br />\n<br />\n針對近日解放軍在台海進行高強度演習，並罕見地派大批戰機飛近海峽中線，胡錫進認為，這說明解放軍已有能力在極短時間內動員組織針對台灣的軍事行動，表明大陸不再容忍美台用切香腸的方式提升勾結。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進指出，大陸全社會已對台當局失去耐心，普遍認為需要給島內台獨勢力一個根本性教訓。他警告，如果台方敢開第一槍攻擊解放軍戰機，那麼解放軍就可以對台開展毀滅性打擊，把解決台灣問題推向新階段。<br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"http://On.CC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOn.CC&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZopriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=c73b6b03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">On.CC</a>"},{"pid":"8788e96fd212783b9b96d9dd920261ae0ea43477","tid":2211863,"uid":231583,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81fb771d4b8d058290687d56bbe99745f8cf8ee8","tid":2211863,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/psfO6Y6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpsfO6Y6.jpg&h=c28e6cbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbd016e48fc496a7cc9332711955315a1104b4c3","tid":2211863,"uid":11097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"他警告，如果台方敢開第一槍攻擊解放軍戰機，那麼解放軍就可以對台開展毀滅性打擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人垛講撚到明唔會<br />\n即係又笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e799e7b1ea224d1a72bab1639db6e08a8452c82","tid":2211863,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb619e1cb7c1d5f3de8ff218c27c404b95479dd7","tid":2211863,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b9377c9c176f55b1aa84e5c8a1cccc67d48a8cc","tid":2211863,"uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HOQATk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HOQATk.gif&h=3d79734e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b31